            <li><strong>Applications:</strong> Telegram, Discord, etc. → Proxy Settings → SOCKS5 → Server: <code>{{ server_host }}</code>, Port: <code>{{ socks_port }}</code></li>
            <li><strong>Command Line:</strong> <code>export ALL_PROXY="socks5://{{ user.username }}:{{ user.password }}@{{ server_host }}:{{ socks_port }}"</code></li>
